1.clone ishkawa/ISNetwork and atebits/OAuthCore.
2.add files to your project.
3.specify CALLBACK_HOST, CONSUMER_KEY and CONSUMER_KEY_SECRET in prefix.pch.
4.show view controller
    example: 
        ISTwitterAuthorizeViewController *viewController = [[ISTwitterAuthorizeViewController alloc] init];
        [self presentModalViewController:viewController animated:YES];
